<h2 id="shellshock"><a href="#shellshock" class="headerlink" title="shellshock"></a>shellshock</h2><h3 id="题目描述-9"><a href="#题目描述-9" class="headerlink" title="题目描述"></a>题目描述</h3><p>Mommy, there was a shocking news about bash.</p>
